{"tid":2463661,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"冇人開我開，一人一間裝修黑店","createTime":"2021-03-27T01:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:40:15.000Z","uid":143724,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"456477bac43b9b02682a5148d259273e4069549d","tid":2463661,"uid":143724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"裝修假假地都幾十萬換嚟一肚氣<br />\n貼錢買難受<br />\n<br />\n由施工期開始驚爛尾驚走數甩期<br />\n到整好收樓後又驚保養唔認帳呢到爆嗰度壞<br />\n做裝修好似大撚晒冇佢符咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如一人一間講吓親身經歷<br />\n警惕新手又好<br />\n踢爆無良黑店又好<br />\n開唔開名釋除尊便<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n以下我會講下我嘅分享<br />\n有親身經歷有聽返嚟"},{"pid":"4da1157dbcaa405ca974efb299cca867f1d19d36","tid":2463661,"uid":23920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:07:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0699767c8b9050a4b616ca105865eeb30e437674","tid":2463661,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0ea7863caabd0f2b190a9ce16c120bf71748c5e9","tid":2463661,"uid":131954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03e3263aefef5c07a4ec46167b29bb167b698138","tid":2463661,"uid":51132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf7f64d2acc25aa956bf37cf0b6532a6393f4c","tid":2463661,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"98b971592aed6cffd071b991e8af677d29b34604","tid":2463661,"uid":143724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"我講第一個啦<br />\n利申親身經歷<br />\n<br />\n裝修時自己買磚買埋啱色嘅掃口粉<br />\n揀磚我哋有貨比三家<br />\n最後都揀番裝修設計師帶過我哋去的磚公司<br />\n<br />\n企缸磚我哋用啡黃色，掃口粉都揀番差唔多啡色<br />\n到收樓檢收時發現企缸部份掃口粉唔同色<br />\n一撻啡撻白色<br />\n投訴先知原來鋪磚時用晒啡色掃口粉<br />\n工